function bindDependencies(derivation) {

    derivation.newObserving = null;

    for (var i = 0; i < l; i++) {
        var dep = observing[i];
        if (dep.diffValue === 0) {
            dep.diffValue = 1;
            if (i0 !== i)
                observing[i0] = dep;
            i0++;
        }
        if (dep.dependenciesState > lowestNewObservingDerivationState) {
            lowestNewObservingDerivationState = dep.dependenciesState;
        }
    }
